  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bae\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bc6\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Don't curse us if Parliament is set on fire - people are rioters.",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "People's revolutionaries have declared that they will never accept Ranil Wickramasinghe, who has been elected by Parliament as the eighth Executive President, as the President of the country.",
        "Accordingly, the protestors held a special press conference at 'Kota Ko Kama' in Kalimugattidal today and announced that they will continue to fight until Ranil Wickremesinghe is ousted and the protest will continue despite the repression.",
        "Today is the 102nd day of the self-insurgency of the people in Kalimuktathidal and the parliament has elected Ranil Wickramasinghe as the 8th executive president and the protesters who participated in the self-insurgency held a media conference together.",
        "Vasantha Mudalike, one of the leading activists of the self-reliance struggle, who participated and commented:",
        "This insurrection caused Gotabaya Rajapaksa, who was elected president with 69 lakh votes, to secretly flee to the Maldives at 3 am.",
        "When this happened, the Lok Sabha was still in session. This protest led to the rejection of Gotabaya Rajapaksa and the removal of Mahinda Rajapaksa from office.",
        "Meanwhile, Ranil Wickramasinghe has been elected as the President in conspiracies within the Parliament using the votes of the expired Podujana Peramuna.",
        "Ranil Wickramasinghe does not have any Lok Sabha. He will be a loser in the 2020 general elections.",
        "Gotabaya Rajapaksa did not make him Prime Minister for the sake of the people who entered the Parliament through the National List.",
        "He was made Prime Minister for the benefit of the Rajapaksa family. That being the case, we will not accept Ranil Wickramasinghe as president without a Lok Sabha.",
        "The people will not stop this struggle until they drive him out. Ranil Wickramasinghe should not think that he can end this struggle by chasing us away, arresting us and shooting us.",
        "Ranil cannot provide any solution to the current problem. Because he has already been the prime minister for 6 times.",
        "His association with central bank policy and incidents like the concentration camp in Patalanda is no secret.",
        "The current parliament does not reflect the will of the people. If people act in violation of Lok Sabha like this, people will set fire to Parliament. If such an incident happens, don't blame it on us and come to us.",
        "It will be clear in two or three weeks what is going to happen to a government that is formed against the will of the people. He said that our struggle will continue."
      ],
